      <div class="text
  
  
  
  js-text
  ">
      <h2 class="
      text__header
      
      
            ">
              Video: What Inspired the Portal Project?
          </h2>
  
      <div class="text__text" ><p>We have just lived through a year like no other. The importance of connecting social justice scholars and movement building organizers has never been greater. Out of conflict and chaos comes some of the most powerful possibilities for change. Together, we will imagine a more just and sustainable future. Check out our video and follow the journey on all social platforms using #SjiPortalProject</p>
</div>
